## DB Schema
MermaidJS
```
classDiagram
    Card <|-- CardControls
    Card <|-- Transactions
    class Card {
        +string card_id
        +string name
        +string number - encrypted
        +string verification_number - encrypted
        +datetime expiry_date
        +datetime valid_from
    }
    class CardControls {
        +string card_control_id
        +string card_id
        +string control_type
        +string control_condition
    }
    class Transactions {
        +string card
        +int amount
        +string merchant
        +string merchant_category
        +boolean approved
    }
```